"ASSAULT CANNONS" "HEAVY WEAPONS" "MACHINE GUNS"

Linked Attribute: ^gStrength^n

Heavy weapons comprise of everything the size of a machine gun or greater.
This includes assault cannons and miniguns aswell as machine guns. You need 
atleast 8 Strength and 8 Body to wield an assault cannon without a mount of 
some kind (either a vehicle or a gyromount).

^WSee Also: GYROMOUNT^n
